'''''Gods, Sound the Anthem of Creation''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Talk to the Astral Express crew
# Talk to Zandar about the Demiurge
# Return the Coreflame and complete the final "Era Nova"

