{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location="Universal Matrix" Great Tomb of the Nameless Titan|update|Amphoreus! I do not beckon your name in haste.<br />I come here to tell a tale of history.<br />When the black tide of doom descended upon Earth, gods fell into madness, and mortals turned against each other.<br />Yet there were Flame-Chasing heroes, pioneering the great enterprise of creating a world.<br /><br />In this world, they shall meld burning golden blood into their bodies.<br />Will the destiny of days to come remember their names?<br /><br />In the name of Worldbearing, I promise you: Kephale will never forget.}}
